STATE
v.
Dorsey Irvin HADDEN. No. 102P06. Supreme Court of North Carolina. April 6, 2006. Bruce T. Cunningham, Jr., Southern Pines, for Dorsy I. Hadden. Ronald L. Moore, District Attorney, for State.

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 2nd day of March 2006 by Attorney General to Dismiss Petition for Writ of Certiorari:

"Motion Dismissed as moot by order of the Court in conference this the 6th day of April 2006."
